" Use jj as Escape
inoremap jj <Esc>

" Hybrid line numbers
set number relativenumber

" Search
set hlsearch " Highlight all search matches
set smartcase " Search is case-insensitive unless caps are present
set incsearch " Highlight matching patterns as search is typed

" Display partial command in status bar
set showcmd

" IntelliJ specific
" First, note u and Ctrl-R automatically use IntelliJ undo/redo

" Join smarter
set ideajoin

" Enable plugins
set surround
set commentary
set argtextobj
set exchange
